---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "Veterinary Clinic Valuation Calculator 2025 | SDE Analysis & Worth";
const description = "Calculate your veterinary clinic worth with our 2025 SDE analysis calculator. Get accurate veterinary practice valuation using proven industry multiples and benchmarks.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
    <div class="article-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1>üêæ Veterinary Clinic Valuation Calculator 2025</h1>
        <p>Complete SDE Analysis & Worth Assessment | Professional Valuation Services</p>
    </div>

    <div class="calculator-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h2>üöÄ Get Your FREE Veterinary Clinic Valuation Now!</h2>
        <p>Calculate your veterinary clinic worth in under 5 minutes using our proven SDE methodology.</p>
        <a href="https://thevaluationgenie.com/" class="cta-button">Calculate My Veterinary Clinic Value</a>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.9;">Free estimate ‚Ä¢ Professional $39 reports available</p>
    </div>

    <article>
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction to Veterinary Clinic Valuation</h2>
            <p>Veterinary clinic valuation is a specialized field that requires deep understanding of veterinary economics, client relationships, equipment depreciation, and industry-specific metrics. In 2025, the veterinary landscape continues evolving with new technologies, changing pet insurance coverage, and increasing corporate consolidation trends.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="sde-analysis">
            <h2>SDE Analysis for Veterinary Clinics</h2>
            <p>Seller's Discretionary Earnings (SDE) is the most accurate method for <strong>veterinary clinic valuation</strong>. Unlike traditional businesses, veterinary clinics have unique financial structures that require specialized analysis.</p>
            <h3>Veterinary Clinic SDE Formula</h3>
            <p><strong>SDE = Net Income + Owner's Salary + Benefits + Depreciation + Interest + Non-recurring Expenses + Owner's Personal Expenses</strong></p>
        </section>
        <section id="faq">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
                <h4>What multiple should I expect for my veterinary clinic?</h4>
                <p>Veterinary clinic multiples typically range from 2.5x to 5.5x SDE, depending on practice type, location, and performance. Small animal practices average 3.0-4.0x SDE, while specialty and emergency practices often achieve 4.0-5.5x SDE.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
                <h4>How do I calculate my practice's SDE?</h4>
                <p>Start with net income and add back owner's salary, benefits, depreciation, interest, and non-recurring expenses. Also add back any personal expenses run through the business.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</MainLayout>
